或交通往來之危險。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/110%2c%e5%af%a9%e7%b0%a1%2c1902%2c20211129%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,110,審簡,1902,20211129,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"審簡","JNO":"1902","JDATE":"20211129","JTITLE":"妨害秩序"}